WEBVTT

00:02.359 --> 00:03.740
Case dismissed.

00:03.741 --> 00:06.051
<i>Previously on "Mistresses"...</i>

00:06.052 --> 00:07.558
That was amazing.

00:07.559 --> 00:09.760
Was that amazing or has
it just been so long?

00:09.761 --> 00:11.269
No. That was amazing.

00:11.270 --> 00:14.881
I saw Paul. I just saw my dead husband.

00:14.882 --> 00:15.775
Hi, April.

00:15.776 --> 00:17.768
- I want a second chance.
- You committed fraud.

00:17.769 --> 00:19.270
Well, I'll turn myself in.

00:19.271 --> 00:24.971
I wanna be with my wife and
my little girl, who I love.

00:26.844 --> 00:29.613
I'm pregnant, Harry, but
it might not be yours.

00:29.614 --> 00:33.183
I don't regret what happened
that night, not for a second.

00:33.184 --> 00:35.819
If the baby isn't mine,
you have a choice to make...

00:35.820 --> 00:38.322
Me or the baby.

00:38.323 --> 00:41.080
This is the results
to my paternity test.

00:41.081 --> 00:44.561
Will you keep this for me?

00:46.000 --> 00:52.074
